tube.com/watch?v=-mnH9-SX2Tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-mnH9-SX2Tg&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=95dd8da8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-mnH9-SX2Tg</a><br />\n<br />\nLily Allen - Three<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C4bWGd4SdtU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC4bWGd4SdtU&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=666bcecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C4bWGd4SdtU</a><br />\n<br />\nAriana Grande - ghostin<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z1pmpDRrQhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZ1pmpDRrQhU&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=42631c9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Z1pmpDRrQhU</a><br />\n<br />\nWeyes Blood - Mirror Forever<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tQ1CH2_Arws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtQ1CH2_Arws&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=35830ec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tQ1CH2_Arws</a><br />\n<br />\nMIKA - Blue<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jR-LQZ-SXd8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjR-LQZ-SXd8&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=0b54fe78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jR-LQZ-SXd8</a>"},{"pid":"02d6eb3f25784a1d8fe084640f2f3917301a2759","tid":1701380,"uid":117584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"Jennifer Hudson 咁出名唔使介紹啦，不過佢翻唱呢首歌都真係好好聽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RUi2Ye6mN-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRUi2Ye6mN-w&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=7be59cdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RUi2Ye6mN-w</a><br />\n<br />\nRegina Belle 阿拉丁嗰首A Whole New World原唱，除咗呢首經典名曲之外佢本身自己個人嘅歌都好好聽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CotwLvu8M5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCotwLvu8M5w&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5db04725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CotwLvu8M5w</a><br />\n<br />\nBarbra Streisand 全球唯一一個係四大界別都攞過大獎嘅人，佢擁有嘅名曲數之不盡但係呢一首歌絕對係當中嘅表表者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/H6Mg1oPhPug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH6Mg1oPhPug&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=fbfd268c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H6Mg1oPhPug</a><br />\n<br />\n一首合唱歌曲，唱嘅四個人都有格林美獎，好聽嘅程度不容置疑啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HyTpu6BmE88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHyTpu6BmE88&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=9353f127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HyTpu6BmE88</a><br />\n<br />\nAnita Baker 一個明明好出名又有幾個格林美獎係身嘅女人，但係唔知點解香港冇人識嘅，把聲圓潤得來又好聽，呢一首係我個人係佢咁多首歌入邊最鍾意嘅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7IwIUYSE5Tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7IwIUYSE5Tg&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=1a521830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7IwIUYSE5Tg</a><br />\n<br />\nPatti LaBelle 都好出名嘅佢係Mariah Carey嘅教母，美國甚至有一條街個街名係用佢個名嚟命名，佢個曲風通常都係輕快丶騷靈同埋福音為多嘅但係呢一首係佢比較算係慢嘅抒情歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cHg-Zkwndqg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcHg-Zkwndqg&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=66028292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cHg-Zkwndqg</a><br />\n<br />\nCyndi Lauper 嘅girls just wanna have fun應該都聽過嘅，呢一首係佢另外嘅首本名曲，非常之出名嘅慢歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VdQY7BusJNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVdQY7BusJNU&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=f6a98235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VdQY7BusJNU</a><br />\n<br />\nEtta James 又係另一個出名到癲嘅女人，早兩輪糖尿病死咗，講嘢都幾串下，不過唱歌都真係幾好聽到呢首歌係佢翻唱經典，再將經典轉化為另一個經典嘅經典名曲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WeoqZ4AUenI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWeoqZ4AUenI&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=6e505002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WeoqZ4AUenI</a><br />\n<br />\nChaka Khan 放克女王，又係好多首本名曲都係輕快嘅，Whitney Houston 嗰一首好出名嘅I&rsquo;m every woman，原唱就係佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-ykVAtOr4mY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-ykVAtOr4mY&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e4da236a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-ykVAtOr4mY</a><br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先，有機會有緣或者你鍾意嘅時候先至再一次介紹其他歌手同音樂俾你"},{"pid":"5ee8b69d0f1f2891e88a461f8b416d83f36ded57","tid":1701380,"uid":77288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:14:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YD6fvzGIBfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYD6fvzGIBfQ&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e109326b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YD6fvzGIBfQ</a>"},{"pid":"c11dfc226c96dde2f14cdfe5f796628e604ea021","tid":1701380,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}